name: Chelsea
summary: Fulham stunned Chelsea 2-1 in a dramatic Premier League encounter on December 26, 2024, dealing a significant blow to the Blues' title aspirations. Cole Palmer set a 23-year Chelsea record in the defeat, while Julen Lopetegui faces scrutiny at West Ham, with only two matches remaining to secure his job. Chelsea's failure to secure a more affordable shirt sponsorship deal has raised questions about their financial strategy. Amidst the turmoil, rumors surface about a falling out between Nkunku and Joao Felix during Chelsea's defeat to Ipswich. Despite speculation, Chelsea plans to recall Anselmino from Boca Juniors. In the lead-up to the Fulham match, Sports Illustrated predicts Chelsea's starting lineup, while We Ain't Got No History provides a comprehensive preview for the Ipswich Town clash. The Guardian reports on Fulham's upset victory over Chelsea, which has halted their title push.

name: Linda Lavin
summary: Linda Lavin, an acclaimed actress known for her roles on Broadway and in the sitcom 'Alice,' has passed away at the age of 87. Lavin, who won a Tony Award for her performance in 'The Diary of Anne Frank,' played the title role in the popular television series 'Alice' from 1976 to 1985. She was also a regular on the sitcom 'Barney Miller' from 1975 to 1979. Lavin's death was due to complications from recently discovered lung cancer. She is remembered as a "beautiful soul" and a talented performer who brought laughter and warmth to audiences for decades.

name: Michael Turner Geelong
summary: The sporting world mourns the passing of Geelong legend Michael Turner at the age of 70 after a prolonged illness. Known as the "legend of Kardinia Park," Turner's impact on football was profound. The Geelong Cats paid tribute to the esteemed talent scout, acknowledging his remarkable contributions. The AFL community expressed its condolences, recognizing Turner's significant impact on the game. In his final days, the Cats bestowed a special recognition upon him, a testament to his enduring legacy. Throughout his career, Turner played a pivotal role in discovering and nurturing the talents of some of the game's greatest players, leaving an unforgettable mark on Australian football.

summary: In Kingaroy, Queensland, heavy rainfall and flooding have caused significant disruptions. An emergency alert was issued for the area, and floodwaters have submerged multiple shops. The severe thunderstorm warning remains in place for parts of Queensland, prompting a "dire" warning from authorities. The flooding is said to be the most severe in 12 years, surpassing the levels seen in 2014. Residents are urged to take precautions and avoid floodwaters.
